# MyWeatherToday — Environment Variables
#
# Current conditions use OpenWeatherMap (station-level accuracy).
# Hourly + 7-day forecast use Open-Meteo (no key needed).
#
# ── Required for current-conditions accuracy ────────────────────────────────
# Get a free key at https://openweathermap.org/api (1,000 calls/day free tier)
OPENWEATHERMAP_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# ── Always free / keyless ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Open-Meteo Weather   → https://api.open-meteo.com
#   Open-Meteo Geocoding → https://geocoding-api.open-meteo.com
#   Nominatim Reverse    → https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your key to enable hybrid mode.
